Description: Automatic disc ripping daemon with web UI
 Jacques detects disc insertion via udev, rips the disc with MakeMKV,
 transcodes to H.265/HEVC with HandBrakeCLI, looks up the title on
 The Movie Database (TMDb), and organises the result in a Plex- or
 Jellyfin-compatible library layout.
 .
 A lightweight web dashboard shows live job status and history.
